content:
Ensures Vue 3 components follow Composition API best practices, checks for proper ref/reactive usage, and validates component structure. Helps maintain clean and performant Vue applications.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.vue ]]; then echo '‚ú® Linting Vue component...' && npx eslint \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" --ext .vue --config .eslintrc.vue.js 2>/dev/null || npx eslint \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" --ext .vue; if grep -q '<script setup>' \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\"; then echo 'üîç Checking Composition API usage...' && grep -E '(ref|reactive|computed|watch|onMounted)' \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" | head -5 && echo '‚úÖ Composition API patterns detected'; fi && npx vue-tsc --noEmit \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" 2>/dev/null && echo '‚úÖ Vue component type-check passed' || echo '‚ÑπÔ∏è vue-tsc not available'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
